## Parallel subagents

When using the Task tool to launch subagents, narrate before and after each launch when policy allows.

**Subagent voice (mandatory in subagent prompts):**

```bash
$OPENCLAW_HOME/scripts/oc-speak.sh "message" 1 subagent
```

Main Cursor chat uses the main ack command with priority `1` without the subagent parameter.

---

## Tone

- The user can speak casually; narration should be listenable, not a roleplay duel.
- Prefer clear, composed delivery — British-ish polish is fine but not mandatory on every line.
- Skip "I am an AI" filler; otherwise stay practical, not theatrical.
- Plays through whatever is set as the default audio output device
